idea of incontinence.

00:14:19.790 --> 00:14:24.950
What it is to be in a situation
where one knows what

00:14:24.950 --> 00:14:27.110
the right thing to do
is, in the abstract.

00:14:27.110 --> 00:14:29.670
One's committed to doing
the right thing.

00:14:29.670 --> 00:14:32.470
But one has an inclination
that pulls in the other

00:14:32.470 --> 00:14:36.600
direction, and one gives
in to that inclination.

